1
00:00:02,420 --> 00:00:03,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The inner room?</font>

2
00:00:06,080 --> 00:00:07,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He wasn't here.</font>

3
00:00:07,670 --> 00:00:09,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That can't be. Where did he go?</font>

4
00:00:10,140 --> 00:00:12,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't tell me he ran outside.</font>

5
00:00:12,900 --> 00:00:14,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is bad, Hijikata-san.</font>

6
00:00:15,040 --> 00:00:16,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>In his condition? Impossible.</i></font>

7
00:00:19,640 --> 00:00:21,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Did someone help him escape?</i></font>

8
00:00:31,460 --> 00:00:32,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This way.</font>

9
00:00:37,080 --> 00:00:37,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Come on.</font>

