<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Georgia">{\an8}<b><font size="60"><font color="#0c6eed">Blue Miburo</font></font></b></font></font>

26
00:00:42,350 --> 00:00:50,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Georgia">{\an8}<b><font size="60"><font color="#0c5ceb">Blue Miburo</font></font></b></font></font>

27
00:00:42,350 --> 00:00:50,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Georgia">{\an8}<b><font size="60"><font color="#0c49ea">Blue Miburo</font></font></b></font></font>

28
00:02:13,240 --> 00:02:20,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah! Yeah, yeah, yeah!</font>

29
00:02:20,040 --> 00:02:22,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Come on, men! Dance!</font>

30
00:02:33,130 --> 00:02:34,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It shows no sign of stopping.</font>

31
00:02:37,280 --> 00:02:39,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Will the swallow take flight?</font>

32
00:02:50,590 --> 00:02:54,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Nio, what are you playing at?</i></font>

33
00:02:55,000 --> 00:02:59,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Don't tell me you plan to help me escape.</i></font>

34
00:03:00,130 --> 00:03:05,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Are you telling me, Serizawa Kamo, 
to turn tail and live on?</i></font>

35
00:03:07,060 --> 00:03:09,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>What would a shameless life get me?</i></font>

36
00:03:09,650 --> 00:03:11,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>What would that leave?</i></font>

37
00:03:11,360 --> 00:03:14,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I have no unfinished business!</i></font>

38
00:03:19,100 --> 00:03:20,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>What the...</i></font>

39
00:03:20,420 --> 00:03:22,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Why the hell am I thinking of you?</i></font>

40
00:03:23,640 --> 00:03:27,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're having a kid? Why should I care?</font>

41
00:03:27,600 --> 00:03:30,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm a samurai.</font>

42
00:03:30,350 --> 00:03:34,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't settle down and start a family.</font>

43
00:03:35,910 --> 00:03:38,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Have it if you want, 
but raise it yourself.</font>

44
00:03:39,560 --> 00:03:40,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What a waste of time.</font>

45
00:03:43,210 --> 00:03:47,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>If that baby was born 
and lived long enough to grow up,</i></font>

46
00:03:47,610 --> 00:03:51,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I guess it would be around their age now.</i></font>

47
00:03:53,220 --> 00:03:57,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>You were the worst of them.</i></font>

48
00:03:58,440 --> 00:04:01,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Always hesitating. 
No faith in yourself.</i></font>

49
00:04:02,300 --> 00:04:04,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Constantly failing.</i></font>

50
00:04:02,470 --> 00:04:02,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><b><font face="Georgia"><font size="18"><font color="#291f18">Manly</font></font></font></b></font>

51
00:04:02,600 --> 00:04:02,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><b><font face="Georgia"><font size="18"><font color="#291f18">Manly</font></font></font></b></font>

52
00:04:02,720 --> 00:04:02,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><b><font face="Georgia"><font size="18"><font color="#291f18">Manly</font></font></font></b></font>

53
00:04:02,850 --> 00:04:02,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><b><font face="Georgia"><font size="18"><font color="#433629">Manly</font></font></font></b></font>

54
00:04:02,970 --> 00:04:03,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><b><font face="Georgia"><font size="18"><font color="#5c4d3e">Manly</font></font></font></b></font>

55
00:04:03,600 --> 00:04:03,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><b><font face="Georgia"><font size="18"><font color="#5c4d3e">Manly</font></font></font></b></font>

56
00:04:03,680 --> 00:04:03,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><b><font face="Georgia"><font size="18"><font color="#5c4d3e">Manly</font></font></font></b></font>

57
00:04:03,770 --> 00:04:03,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><b><font face="Georgia"><font size="18"><font color="#5c4d3e">Manly</font></font></font></b></font>

58
00:04:04,790 --> 00:04:07,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Always worrying 
what other people think.</i></font>

59
00:04:09,420 --> 00:04:13,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>You couldn't be farther 
from Serizawa Kamo's ideal man.</i></font>

60
00:04:17,600 --> 00:04:20,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Bah! Now I've got myself pissed off!</i></font>

61
00:04:20,360 --> 00:04:23,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I want to give him a good thump
 and kick right now!</i></font>

62
00:04:29,490 --> 00:04:32,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Come here. I'll give you a bath.</font>

63
00:04:37,070 --> 00:04:39,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I thought I picked him up on a whim...</i></font>

64
00:04:39,880 --> 00:04:44,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font color="#ffffff"><font color="#f4f4f4">You good-for-nothing! 
Can't you even pour tea right?</font></font></font>

65
00:04:44,120 --> 00:04:47,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>...and came down so hard on him...</i></font>

66
00:04:47,530 --> 00:04:50,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Taro, put more oomph in your step.</font>

67
00:04:50,110 --> 00:04:51,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Y-Yes, sir.</font>

68
00:04:52,100 --> 00:04:57,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>...because I felt guilty about 
not looking after my own kid.</i></font>

69
00:04:59,220 --> 00:05:02,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But if I was doing it to atone,</i></font>

70
00:05:05,570 --> 00:05:11,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>would it have killed me 
to give him a hug just once?</i></font>

71
00:05:15,130 --> 00:05:17,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Will I survive this?</i></font>

72
00:05:18,180 --> 00:05:20,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Is that future possible?</i></font>

73
00:05:22,590 --> 00:05:23,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'll live.</i></font>

74
00:05:25,200 --> 00:05:26,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I want to live.</i></font>

75
00:05:41,710 --> 00:05:45,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Serizawa-san, I have kept you
 waiting for far too long.</font>

76
00:05:50,970 --> 00:05:51,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Death.</i></font>

77
00:05:54,810 --> 00:05:56,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Take my head.</font>

78
00:05:59,920 --> 00:06:02,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I hope I can trust you to do it properly.</font>

79
00:06:02,960 --> 00:06:04,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Who do you think you're talking to?</font>

80
00:06:11,530 --> 00:06:16,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Show me a death
worthy of Serizawa Kamo.</font>

81
00:06:21,720 --> 00:06:23,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>No.</i></font>

82
00:06:23,190 --> 00:06:25,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>What am I thinking?</i></font>

83
00:06:25,570 --> 00:06:30,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Isn't this the future 
I wanted more than any other?</i></font>

84
00:06:38,440 --> 00:06:43,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You said it. How I've waited 
for this, Sir Kondo.</font>

85
00:06:44,640 --> 00:06:46,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A friend of mine died.</font>

86
00:06:48,010 --> 00:06:51,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If your death leads to the future...</font>

87
00:06:52,650 --> 00:06:54,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Did he take his own life?</font>

88
00:06:55,080 --> 00:06:55,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes.</font>

89
00:06:56,280 --> 00:06:59,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But he left many things behind.</font>

90
00:07:03,720 --> 00:07:05,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wh-Who the hell are you?</font>

91
00:07:05,520 --> 00:07:09,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Can't you even tell friend from foe?!</font>

92
00:07:11,270 --> 00:07:12,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let us through.</font>

93
00:07:20,620 --> 00:07:22,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Leave it to a real samurai.</font>

94
00:07:22,730 --> 00:07:25,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Where would the Miburo be without you?</font>

95
00:07:26,670 --> 00:07:28,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I won't lead you wrong.</font>

96
00:07:28,860 --> 00:07:31,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He was an extraordinarily clever man.</font>

97
00:07:30,760 --> 00:07:30,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font face="Georgia"><b><font color="#2a2c2d">Bylaws</font></b></font></font>

98
00:07:30,800 --> 00:07:30,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font face="Georgia"><b><font color="#2a2c2d">Bylaws</font></b></font></font>

99
00:07:30,930 --> 00:07:31,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font face="Georgia"><b><font color="#2a2c2d">Bylaws</font></b></font></font>

100
00:07:31,050 --> 00:07:31,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font face="Georgia"><b><font color="#2a2c2d">Bylaws</font></b></font></font>

101
00:07:31,180 --> 00:07:31,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font face="Georgia"><b><font color="#2a2c2d">Bylaws</font></b></font></font>

102
00:07:31,310 --> 00:07:31,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font face="Georgia"><b><font color="#2a2c2d">Bylaws</font></b></font></font>

103
00:07:31,430 --> 00:07:31,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font face="Georgia"><b><font color="#2a2c2d">Bylaws</font></b></font></font>

104
00:07:31,560 --> 00:07:31,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font face="Georgia"><b><font color="#2a2c2d">Bylaws</font></b></font></font>

105
00:07:31,680 --> 00:07:32,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font face="Georgia"><b><font color="#2a2c2d">Bylaws</font></b></font></font>

106
00:07:31,900 --> 00:07:34,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yamanami, I want you to have this.</font>

107
00:07:38,980 --> 00:07:40,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What are you thinking?</font>

108
00:07:40,900 --> 00:07:43,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I won't dance to your tune.</font>

109
00:07:50,020 --> 00:07:52,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Welcome.</font>

110
00:07:52,620 --> 00:07:56,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I wonder just how much
 of this he planned.</font>

111
00:07:57,600 --> 00:07:58,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That doesn't matter!</font>

112
00:07:59,120 --> 00:08:03,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It has nothing to do with us at all!</font>

113
00:08:03,380 --> 00:08:05,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please calm yourself and listen.</font>

114
00:08:06,540 --> 00:08:09,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This isn't only relevant to us. 
You also have—</font>

115
00:08:09,290 --> 00:08:10,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No!</font>

116
00:08:10,390 --> 00:08:11,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, never!</font>

117
00:08:11,640 --> 00:08:13,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I won't move from this spot!</font>

118
00:08:15,380 --> 00:08:18,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Quit your whining, you insufferable bitch!</font>

119
00:08:19,490 --> 00:08:21,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, dear. I lost my temper.</font>

120
00:08:24,150 --> 00:08:26,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I sent Itosato to Fushimi.</font>

121
00:08:26,800 --> 00:08:28,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What? Ito-chan is safe?</font>

122
00:08:28,920 --> 00:08:31,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Join her and leave Kyoto.</font>

123
00:08:31,740 --> 00:08:36,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Won't you please try 
to start new lives in peace?</font>

124
00:08:45,920 --> 00:08:48,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I assume you can find
 your way from here?</font>

125
00:08:49,690 --> 00:08:50,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes.</font>

126
00:08:52,450 --> 00:08:56,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The Miburo's future 
hinges on this mission.</i></font>

127
00:08:56,830 --> 00:09:01,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Our involvement must never come to light.</i></font>

128
00:09:02,610 --> 00:09:04,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>We cannot allow Hirama to escape.</i></font>

129
00:09:05,630 --> 00:09:08,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'm counting on you, Harada-san.</i></font>

130
00:09:10,040 --> 00:09:11,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Get back here, Hirama!</font>

131
00:09:12,150 --> 00:09:15,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Fight me fair and square!</font>

132
00:09:15,360 --> 00:09:18,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't you want to fight for Serizawa?</font>

133
00:09:18,170 --> 00:09:20,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What kind of friend are you?</font>

134
00:09:27,800 --> 00:09:29,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you crying?</font>

135
00:09:29,510 --> 00:09:31,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is <i>this</i> how you repay him?!</font>

136
00:09:31,220 --> 00:09:32,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

137
00:09:32,400 --> 00:09:36,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't forget! The Miburo wouldn't be 
who they are now without Serizawa-sensei.</font>

138
00:09:36,520 --> 00:09:39,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">None of you appreciate 
his real significance!</font>

139
00:09:39,050 --> 00:09:42,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Losing him would be a blow to the nation!</font>

140
00:09:42,720 --> 00:09:44,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Isn't that laying it on a bit thick?</i></font>

141
00:09:45,330 --> 00:09:49,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Harada, you picked 
the wrong man to follow.</font>

142
00:09:49,200 --> 00:09:51,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I decide who I throw my weight behind.</font>

143
00:09:53,540 --> 00:09:54,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's fighting dirty!</font>

144
00:09:54,500 --> 00:09:55,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Die!</font>

145
00:09:56,490 --> 00:09:57,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No chance!</font>

146
00:09:58,530 --> 00:10:02,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll expose your wickedness to the world.</font>

147
00:10:02,120 --> 00:10:03,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You'll what?</font>

148
00:10:06,800 --> 00:10:08,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't you forget it!</font>

149
00:10:19,090 --> 00:10:21,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Damn it. Where'd you go?</font>

150
00:10:21,020 --> 00:10:24,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Say something! 
Get out here, Hirama!</font>

151
00:10:28,610 --> 00:10:32,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">C-Crap. I've totally lost him.</font>

152
00:10:37,900 --> 00:10:39,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What? What happened?</font>

153
00:11:02,960 --> 00:11:04,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What the hell...</font>

154
00:11:06,430 --> 00:11:09,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Shimada, bury him deep.</font>

155
00:11:12,600 --> 00:11:13,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Shinpachi.</font>

156
00:11:14,310 --> 00:11:16,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I still don't approve of your methods.</font>

157
00:11:18,950 --> 00:11:21,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yet I have no choice 
but to carry this secret to my grave.</font>

158
00:11:23,340 --> 00:11:26,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I cannot allow you 
to shoulder the burden alone.</font>

159
00:11:26,970 --> 00:11:29,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Allow me to share the blame.</font>

160
00:11:34,380 --> 00:11:35,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's wrong?</font>

161
00:11:35,250 --> 00:11:35,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nothing.</font>

162
00:11:37,090 --> 00:11:39,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I only wondered what my pupil was up to.</font>

163
00:11:53,120 --> 00:11:54,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your lunges need work.</font>

164
00:11:55,440 --> 00:11:56,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Screw you!</font>

165
00:11:59,430 --> 00:12:03,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is that it? Is that how much
 you care about Serizawa?</font>

166
00:12:10,720 --> 00:12:12,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Let it all out.</i></font>

167
00:12:12,580 --> 00:12:15,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'll make you spew your heart out...</i></font>

168
00:12:15,500 --> 00:12:18,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>till you've got no dregs 
of regret left in you.</i></font>

169
00:12:21,710 --> 00:12:23,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is the Yagi residence.</font>

170
00:12:23,410 --> 00:12:25,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's the Miburo's base of operations.</font>

171
00:12:30,060 --> 00:12:31,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's Taro-kun.</font>

172
00:12:31,460 --> 00:12:35,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He does... all sorts 
of odd jobs around here.</font>

173
00:12:36,420 --> 00:12:38,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>When I met him,</i></font>

174
00:12:38,250 --> 00:12:43,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>he looked so lifeless that I couldn't tell
what he was thinking.</i></font>

175
00:12:48,620 --> 00:12:50,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm going drinking.</font>

176
00:12:50,180 --> 00:12:54,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>He followed Serizawa around like a puppy.</i></font>

177
00:12:51,810 --> 00:12:54,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Sensei! Y-Your coat.</font>

178
00:12:55,040 --> 00:12:56,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Hurry up with it!</font>

179
00:12:57,800 --> 00:13:01,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But before I knew it, 
he'd become a good worker.</i></font>

180
00:13:05,730 --> 00:13:07,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Take care of mine, too.</font>

181
00:13:09,010 --> 00:13:10,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, be seeing you.</font>

182
00:13:14,730 --> 00:13:15,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Jackass.</font>

183
00:13:17,650 --> 00:13:21,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>He cursed everyone 
but Serizawa behind their backs.</i></font>

184
00:13:22,120 --> 00:13:23,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But then, Nio came.</i></font>

185
00:13:24,760 --> 00:13:26,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Taro-kun, do you want 
to practice sumo with us?</font>

186
00:13:26,920 --> 00:13:28,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No way in hell!</font>

187
00:13:29,610 --> 00:13:31,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hurry up!</font>

188
00:13:31,010 --> 00:13:34,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>He seemed livelier after that.</i></font>

189
00:13:34,790 --> 00:13:37,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I doubt he even considered 
learning the sword.</i></font>

190
00:13:37,240 --> 00:13:38,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But then...</i></font>

191
00:13:40,120 --> 00:13:43,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Just recently, he started 
taking lessons from Nagakura.</i></font>

192
00:13:44,050 --> 00:13:45,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Even so...</i></font>

193
00:13:48,480 --> 00:13:49,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Damn it!</font>

194
00:13:48,480 --> 00:13:50,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>His center of balance is off.</i></font>

195
00:13:50,740 --> 00:13:52,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>And he swings with his arms.</i></font>

196
00:13:53,100 --> 00:13:55,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>He doesn't have close to enough training.</i></font>

197
00:13:56,400 --> 00:13:57,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But in spite of that,</i></font>

198
00:13:59,350 --> 00:14:02,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>look how much stronger having 
something to protect has made him.</i></font>

199
00:14:05,240 --> 00:14:09,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If I don't get to Serizawa-sensei,
 he'll... he'll...</font>

200
00:14:11,300 --> 00:14:14,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You couldn't do anything 
even if you were with him!</font>

201
00:14:14,270 --> 00:14:16,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Move! Let me through!</font>

202
00:14:16,150 --> 00:14:18,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why are you so hung up on Serizawa?!</font>

203
00:14:18,710 --> 00:14:24,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The Yagis and Kondo's gang 
have done just as much for you!</font>

204
00:14:25,960 --> 00:14:27,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And don't forget Nio.</font>

205
00:14:28,590 --> 00:14:29,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Or me.</font>

206
00:14:29,650 --> 00:14:31,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You guys don't get it.</font>

207
00:14:32,520 --> 00:14:33,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">When Sensei...</font>

208
00:14:36,320 --> 00:14:40,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Before he faces everyone, 
he pauses, just for a moment.</font>

209
00:14:43,890 --> 00:14:48,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's the time it takes him 
to become Serizawa Kamo.</font>

210
00:14:53,460 --> 00:14:56,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Only I know about it, 
because I followed him around.</font>

211
00:14:56,720 --> 00:15:00,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I like that about him, 
and I respect him for it.</font>

212
00:15:02,610 --> 00:15:04,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He likes living it up in a big group,</font>

213
00:15:05,140 --> 00:15:07,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and when he ate 
and drank with everybody,</font>

214
00:15:08,420 --> 00:15:10,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">he looked truly happy!</font>

215
00:15:14,970 --> 00:15:17,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He spent so much time 
surrounded by people.</font>

216
00:15:20,910 --> 00:15:24,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But I'm sure he plans to die alone.</font>

217
00:15:27,480 --> 00:15:33,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So why shouldn't someone stick with him
 to the end, even it it's only me?</font>

218
00:15:42,360 --> 00:15:43,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You moron.</font>

219
00:15:44,600 --> 00:15:47,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You really are as stupid as they come.</font>

220
00:15:51,430 --> 00:15:54,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I can't keep going much longer. 
And I'm out of time.</i></font>

221
00:15:56,140 --> 00:15:57,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>This is good enough, right?</i></font>

222
00:15:59,340 --> 00:16:04,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Listen, in a real fight, hold your sword 
to make it as short as you can in.</font>

223
00:16:04,650 --> 00:16:08,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sh-Short? But then, it won't reach.</font>

224
00:16:08,790 --> 00:16:11,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wouldn't that put me 
at a huge disadvantage?</font>

225
00:16:11,570 --> 00:16:14,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No matter. Fight like that.</font>

226
00:16:15,100 --> 00:16:17,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This swallow is but one bird.</font>

227
00:16:17,370 --> 00:16:19,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You must scatter feed before its flight.</font>

228
00:16:27,220 --> 00:16:29,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Nagakura, I'm gonna use it.</i></font>

229
00:16:34,280 --> 00:16:36,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>What is that stance?</i></font>

230
00:16:36,580 --> 00:16:39,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Is that his idea of 
a secret weapon? Idiot.</i></font>

231
00:16:40,480 --> 00:16:42,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>You'll never reach me from there.</i></font>

232
00:16:42,570 --> 00:16:44,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Don't you even know your own range?</i></font>

233
00:16:48,280 --> 00:16:50,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font color="#ffffff"><font color="#f4f4f4">You're forgetting someone.</font></font></font>

234
00:16:51,560 --> 00:16:52,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Taro.</font>

235
00:16:52,910 --> 00:16:56,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He'll stick with Serizawa 
to the bitter end.</font>

236
00:16:57,450 --> 00:16:59,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hajime, he's your job.</font>

237
00:17:00,060 --> 00:17:01,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You want me to kill him?</font>

238
00:17:01,870 --> 00:17:05,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't even joke about that!
In that case, <i>you</i> handle Taro!</font>

239
00:17:05,120 --> 00:17:06,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'll</i> kill Serizawa.</font>

240
00:17:07,560 --> 00:17:08,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't mean that.</font>

241
00:17:10,120 --> 00:17:11,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What, then?</font>

242
00:17:13,590 --> 00:17:15,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I want you to save Taro.</font>

243
00:17:17,920 --> 00:17:19,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Shut up.</i></font>

244
00:17:20,600 --> 00:17:21,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's really coming down, huh?</font>

245
00:17:24,200 --> 00:17:25,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I wonder if it'll stop by tonight.</font>

246
00:17:26,290 --> 00:17:27,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Beats me.</font>

247
00:17:30,630 --> 00:17:33,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do your best for Taro-kun.</font>

248
00:17:37,680 --> 00:17:39,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I know that.</i></font>

249
00:17:40,020 --> 00:17:42,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>And with all of it in mind,</i></font>

250
00:17:45,600 --> 00:17:47,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'll make him wish he'd never crossed me!</i></font>

251
00:17:53,210 --> 00:17:58,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You've only just started training. 
You can't defeat a master in a fair fight.</font>

252
00:17:59,290 --> 00:18:04,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your enemy will soon learn 
to gauge your range.</font>

253
00:18:04,870 --> 00:18:09,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Therefore, shift your right hand down 
without revealing your grip.</font>

254
00:18:11,230 --> 00:18:14,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">As close to the pommel
as you can manage.</font>

255
00:18:14,470 --> 00:18:18,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thus, your blade will grow 
one hand-width longer.</font>

256
00:18:19,230 --> 00:18:22,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And then, the swallow will soar.</font>

257
00:18:31,920 --> 00:18:32,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Swallow.</font>

258
00:18:41,810 --> 00:18:42,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I missed!</i></font>

259
00:18:46,380 --> 00:18:50,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If your enemy strikes first, 
draw without hesitation as he pulls back.</font>

260
00:18:51,120 --> 00:18:52,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Learn with your body.</font>

261
00:18:53,440 --> 00:18:55,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Make drawing your sword a reflex.</font>

262
00:18:56,210 --> 00:18:59,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That blade will keep you safe.</font>

263
00:19:01,640 --> 00:19:02,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Strike back.</font>

264
00:19:02,820 --> 00:19:04,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>No. Stop!</i></font>

265
00:19:05,310 --> 00:19:06,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Dodge!</i></font>

266
00:19:09,700 --> 00:19:11,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Please dodge!</i></font>

267
00:19:26,600 --> 00:19:28,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Too slow.</font>

268
00:19:28,060 --> 00:19:30,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're much too slow, Sir Kondo.</font>

269
00:19:31,100 --> 00:19:34,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now, I think it's time 
we put an end to this.</font>

270
00:19:34,980 --> 00:19:36,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, Serizawa-san.</font>

271
00:19:43,880 --> 00:19:45,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Prepare to die!</font>

272
00:19:59,010 --> 00:20:03,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's the Kondo I know. Well struck.</font>

273
00:20:12,190 --> 00:20:13,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Niimi-san.</font>

274
00:20:13,890 --> 00:20:15,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">May I ask you one final thing?</font>

275
00:20:16,320 --> 00:20:20,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You and Serizawa-san have gone about
 causing mischief for a long time.</font>

276
00:20:21,140 --> 00:20:25,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Serizawa-san grows bored easily, 
causes trouble, and then moves on.</font>

277
00:20:26,440 --> 00:20:30,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But you told me you've come 
to like Kyoto and the Miburo,</font>

278
00:20:31,520 --> 00:20:33,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and you wish to stay with us longer.</font>

279
00:20:34,440 --> 00:20:38,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What exactly sets the Miburo apart 
from all that came before?</font>

280
00:20:40,360 --> 00:20:41,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Serizawa was different.</font>

281
00:20:44,800 --> 00:20:48,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He was the big-hearted, 
jovial version of himself that I liked.</font>

282
00:20:49,720 --> 00:20:54,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Maybe finding an equal for the first time 
took a weight off his shoulders.</font>

283
00:20:58,320 --> 00:21:00,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You mean...</font>

284
00:21:00,280 --> 00:21:00,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes.</font>

285
00:21:02,910 --> 00:21:05,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm nothing but grateful to him.</font>

286
00:21:24,810 --> 00:21:27,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>No. I'm going to see this through.</i></font>

287
00:21:29,360 --> 00:21:33,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Watch to the end and never forget.</i></font>

288
00:21:34,680 --> 00:21:36,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>This is Serizawa-san.</i></font>

289
00:21:41,660 --> 00:21:42,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>This is...</i></font>

290
00:21:43,580 --> 00:21:45,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Serizawa Kamo.</i></font>

291
00:21:44,190 --> 00:21:49,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font face="Georgia"><b><font size="40">Serizawa Kamo</font></b></font></font>

292
00:23:20,080 --> 00:23:25,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="TImes New Roman"><font size="26"><b>{\an8}Next time</b></font></font></font>

293
00:23:21,150 --> 00:23:25,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Niimi—no, Iori, it's almost time.</font>

294
00:23:26,560 --> 00:23:30,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I promised you a finale worthy
 of Serizawa Kamo.</font>

295
00:23:31,130 --> 00:23:33,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, the end is closing in now.</font>

296
00:23:34,050 --> 00:23:36,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I have no remorse. No regrets.</font>

297
00:23:37,040 --> 00:23:40,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I didn't leave any unfinished business.</font>

298
00:23:40,190 --> 00:23:42,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Can you see this, Nio?</font>

299
00:23:42,650 --> 00:23:45,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is the future I wanted
 more than any other.</font>

300
00:23:46,590 --> 00:23:49,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Next time: "Blue Era."</font>

301
00:23:47,110 --> 00:23:49,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font face="Georgia"><b><font size="40">Blue Era</font></b></font></font>

